verbose_text: Following a one hour incubation in co-cultures containing MUC1 expressing (HES) and non expressing (HS-5) human cell lines at 37oC, the MUC1 directed particles demonstrated high specificity and accumulation in the targeted HES cells, while low particle binding was observed in HS-5 cells.
evidence: MUC1-directed particles demonstrated high specificity and accumulation in the targeted HES
